---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="What is GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)? Complete Guide | GeoScore"
  schema={{
    '@context': 'https://schema.org',
    '@type': 'Article',
    headline: 'What is GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)? Complete Guide',
    description: 'Complete guide to Generative Engine Optimization (GEO) — optimizing your website for AI search engines like ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Google AI Overviews.',
    url: 'https://geoscore.help/blog/what-is-geo/',
    datePublished: '2025-07-01',
    author: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'GeoScore' },
    publisher: { '@type': 'Organization', name: 'GeoScore', url: 'https://geoscore.help' }
  }}
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-geo-500/10 text-geo-400 border border-geo-500/20 mb-4">
          GEO Guide
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-3">What is GEO (Generative Engine Optimization)?</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Published July 2025 · 8 min read</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6">
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-4">
          <strong class="text-white">Generative Engine Optimization (GEO)</strong> is the practice of optimizing your website so that AI-powered search engines — like ChatGPT, Perplexity, Google AI Overviews, and Claude — can discover, understand, and cite your content.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          If traditional SEO is about ranking #1 on Google, GEO is about being the source AI engines quote when users ask questions.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Why GEO Matters Now</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          AI search is exploding. By 2025, over <strong class="text-white">1 billion people</strong> use AI search engines monthly. Perplexity alone handles 100M+ queries per day. Google now shows AI Overviews for a large share of searches.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400">
          If your site isn't optimized for AI discovery, you're invisible to this growing audience. GEO ensures your content is crawlable, understandable, and citable by AI models.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">GEO vs. Traditional SEO</h2>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm">
            <thead><tr class="border-b border-gray-700 text-left">
              <th class="pb-3 pr-4 text-gray-300">Aspect</th>
              <th class="pb-3 pr-4 text-gray-300">Traditional SEO</th>
              <th class="pb-3 text-gray-300">GEO</th>
            </tr></thead>
            <tbody class="text-gray-400">
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Target</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Google, Bing rankings</td><td class="py-2">ChatGPT, Perplexity, AI Overviews</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Crawlers</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Googlebot, Bingbot</td><td class="py-2">GPTBot, ClaudeBot, PerplexityBot</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Discovery</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Sitemap, backlinks</td><td class="py-2">llms.txt, AI endpoints, schema</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Content format</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Keyword-optimized</td><td class="py-2">Citation-ready, structured</td></tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-gray-700/50"><td class="py-2 pr-4">Success metric</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">Rank position, CTR</td><td class="py-2">Citation frequency, brand mention</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 pr-4">Key file</td><td class="py-2 pr-4">robots.txt</td><td class="py-2">llms.txt + robots.txt</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">12 Dimensions of GEO Readiness</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
          <li><strong class="text-white">AI Crawlability</strong> — Is your robots.txt allowing AI crawlers?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">AI Guidance</strong> — Do you have an llms.txt file?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Structured Data</strong> — Is your content marked up with schema.org?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Meta & Social Tags</strong> — Are your meta tags complete?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Content Quality</strong> — Is your content substantial and well-structured?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">E-E-A-T Signals</strong> — Do you show Experience, Expertise, Authority, Trust?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Brand & Entity</strong> — Is your brand recognizable to AI?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Citation Readiness</strong> — Can AI easily cite your content?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Discovery Endpoints</strong> — Do you have AI-specific endpoints?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Agent-Friendliness</strong> — Can AI agents interact with your site?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Freshness</strong> — Is your content up to date?</li>
          <li><strong class="text-white">Negative Signals</strong> — Any factors that hurt AI visibility?</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">How to Get Started</h2>
        <ol class="space-y-3 text-gray-400">
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">1.</strong> Run a free <a href="/" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">GEO audit</a> to get your baseline score</li>
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">2.</strong> Check your <a href="/tools/robots-txt-ai-checker" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">robots.txt</a> isn't blocking AI crawlers</li>
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">3.</strong> Create an <a href="/tools/llms-txt-checker" class="text-brand-500 hover:underline">llms.txt file</a> for your site</li>
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">4.</strong> Add structured data (JSON-LD) to key pages</li>
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">5.</strong> Improve content with citations, stats, and clear structure</li>
          <li><strong class="text-geo-500">6.</strong> Re-audit monthly to track your score</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="card p-8 mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-geo-500/10 to-brand-500/10 border border-brand-500/20">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to Check Your GEO Score?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">Get a free 12-dimension audit with actionable recommendations.</p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-geo-600 to-brand-600 hover:from-geo-500 hover:to-brand-500 transition">
          Start Free GEO Audit →
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
